sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant UI as TemplateBrowserModal
    participant Hook as useAgentTemplates
    participant Tauri as Tauri Commands
    participant Rust as Rust Backend
    participant FS as File System

    User->>UI: Click "Browse Templates"
    UI->>Hook: listTemplates()
    Hook->>Tauri: list_agent_templates()
    Tauri->>Rust: Load templates.json
    Rust->>FS: Read template metadata
    FS-->>Rust: templates[]
    Rust-->>Tauri: templates[]
    Tauri-->>Hook: templates
    Hook-->>UI: templates
    UI-->>User: Show template cards

    User->>UI: Click "Import"
    UI->>Hook: importTemplate(templateId)
    Hook->>Tauri: import_agent_template(id)
    Tauri->>Rust: Import handler
    Rust->>FS: Create agent directory
    Rust->>FS: Copy SOUL.md + IDENTITY.md
    Rust->>FS: Write config entry
    FS-->>Rust: Success
    Rust-->>Tauri: New agent
    Tauri-->>Hook: agent
    Hook-->>UI: Close modal
    UI-->>User: Success toast
